        <h2>Snow </h2>
        <h4> Snow is one of the biggest things Canada is known for. Each winter, snow falls in great quantities all over the contry. Places like the east coast tend to get less snow due to temperature differences because of streams in the oceans or because of how close to the equater certain places are. The snowfall can get to such a high level that some days, whole cities will be told to work from home rather than attempt to go outside. Although the snow is a lot to take in at first, you'll get use to it fast because deep down, everyone loves playing in it. </h4>
        
